text:
Olajide Olayinka Williams "JJ" Olatunji (born 19 June 1993), best known as KSI, is an English YouTuber, rapper and boxer. He was born in London, he has a brother called Deji who also is an entertainer.
KSI was ranked as the second most influential online creator in the United Kingdom by The Times. He had a boxing match with Logan Paul.
His name “KSI” stands for Knowledge, Strength, Integrity.
He is of Nigerian descent.
